Thing's only got a few good games(but all with bad audio issues, holy jebus) and a buncha shovelware to pad the title roster to boast that impressive sounding 50+ game list. Infinitely better value and use than the crummy 50 dollar knockoff Genesis. Lol.

My whole point here? Bobby should got a point for that smash.
